input.value:
fetch events
 | filter event.kind=="SECURITY_EVENT" and event.category=="VULNERABILITY_MANAGEMENT" and event.provider=="Dynatrace" 
     and event.type=="VULNERABILITY_STATE_REPORT_EVENT" and  event.level=="ENTITY" and vulnerability.stack == "CODE_LIBRARY"
 | filter in("All","All") OR in(affected_entity.management_zones.names,"All")
 | filter event.status == "OPEN" and vulnerability.mute.status == "NOT_MUTED"
 | sort timestamp desc
 | summarize by:{ID=vulnerability.display_id, pg=affected_entity.id}, {
 `Process IDs`=takeFirst( affected_entity.affected_processes.ids),
 Last_update=takeFirst(timestamp), 
 Description=takeFirst(event.description), 
 Score=takeFirst(vulnerability.parent.davis_assessment.score), 
 Level=takeFirst(vulnerability.parent.davis_assessment.level),
 Title=takeFirst(vulnerability.title),
 Status=takeFirst(vulnerability.status),
 CVE=takeFirst(vulnerability.reference.cve),
 Technology=takeFirst(vulnerability.technology),
 URL=takeFirst(vulnerability.url),
 `Public Exposure`=takeFirst(vulnerability.parent.davis_assessment.exposure_status),
 `Reachable Data`=takeFirst(vulnerability.parent.davis_assessment.data_assets_status),
 `Vulnerable Function`=takeFirst(vulnerability.parent.davis_assessment.vulnerable_function_status),
 Muted=takeFirst(vulnerability.mute_status),
 MZ=takeFirst(affected_entity.management_zones.names)
 }
 | expand pid=`Process IDs`
 | lookup [fetch dt.entity.process_group_instance
    | fields process_id=id, process_name=entity.name, host_id=belongs_to[dt.entity.host]
    | lookup [ fetch dt.entity.host | fieldsAdd ipAddress], sourceField:host_id, lookupField:id, fields:{host_name=entity.name,ip=ipAddress}]
    , sourceField:pid, lookupField:process_id, fields:{process_id,process_name, host_id, host_name, ip}
 | fields ID, host_name, ip, process_name, Score, Level, Title, `Public Exposure`, `Reachable Data`, `Vulnerable Function`, URL
 | sort Score desc
